`8Ka`&i`8n``~
`8Ka`&i`8n`` floats here, freed from his subspace prison.
~
`8Ka`&i`8n``'s "skin" is a seething pitch-black mass, undulating 
in it's absorbtion of light. He has broken free of his subspace 
prison to gain revenge against the Jurai, who helped imprison him 
there. `8Ka`&i`8n`` is a being of great age, and great power, and 
has destroyed countless worlds and civilizations. He is to be feared.
~
