#ROOMS
#12300
On a platform~
The wind drives the dusty, dirty air of Neo Tokyo  across the 
large platform you're standing on, blowing leaves that had 
settled here off. In the four corners of the platform stand 
large machienes, with four beams of light pointed at the center, 
creating a large portal.
~
0 4 1
D2
~
~
