S
#12301
On a telepad~
Eight points of light from all eight corners of the room send 
beams at perfect 45 degree angles into the center of the room, 
creating a large vortex like portal. A light wind pours through 
the portal, bringing dirty air and the stench of smog into 
the room.
~
